            </div>
            <div class="w-full h-px bg-zinc mt-3"></div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div data-action="click->accordion#toggle" data-accordion-target="accTitle" id="acc_btn" data-id="acc_btn2" data-active="false" class="acc_title flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer">
              <p class="font-medium pt-5 pb-3 text-dark-grey">
                Characteristics
              </p>
              <div data-accordion-target="accordionIcon" class="mt-3"></div>
            </div>
            <a class="hidden pt-3 text-dark-blue">
              <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Suspendisse in est pharetra, accumsan quam in, ornare ante. Integer volutpat ipsum ut consectetur aliquam. Donec sit amet efficitur metus, vitae hendrerit justo. Vivamus dapibus nunc id egestas posuere. Nulla gravida lorem sit amet varius tincidunt. Fusce elementum purus orci, sed dictum erat efficitur eget. Vestibulum quis elementum est.</p>
            </a>
            <div class="w-full h-px bg-zinc mt-3"></div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div data-action="click->accordion#toggle" data-accordion-target="accTitle" id="acc_btn" data-id="acc_btn3" data-active="false" class="acc_title flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer">
              <p class="font-medium pt-5 pb-3 text-dark-grey">
                Delivery and returns
              </p>
              <div data-accordion-target="accordionIcon" class="mt-3"></div>
            </div>
            <a class="hidden pt-3 text-dark-blue">
              <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Suspendisse in est pharetra, accumsan quam in, ornare ante. Integer volutpat ipsum ut consectetur aliquam. Donec sit amet efficitur metus, vitae hendrerit justo. Vivamus dapibus nunc id egestas posuere. Nulla gravida lorem sit amet varius tincidunt. Fusce elementum purus orci, sed dictum erat efficitur eget. Vestibulum quis elementum est.</p>
            </a>
            <div class="w-full h-px bg-zinc mt-3"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 flex justify-center items-center md:order-2 order-1">
      <div class="w-2/3">
        <%= image_tag(@product.main_picture) %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="w-full max-w-screen-2xl lg:mx-auto pb-14 pl-7 mt-24 md:pl-24 overflow-hidden">
  <h4 class="text-2xl text-gray-800 mb-7 font-medium normal-case">Other products</h4>
  <div class="relative w-full overflow-x-auto pb-5">
    <div class="w-[110rem] pr-12 flex justify-between items-center">
      <% @suggest_products.each do |product| %>
        <%= render partial: "suggest_products", locals: { product: product } %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
